title: Ep 2494 - Investment Woes
shortDesc: Jethalal, Taarak, Bhide, and Popatlal discuss the best options to invest their money in. Bhide agrees that bank to be the best option and is ecstatic that his invested money is growing. Later, Taarak reads in the newspaper about a banking scam.

title: Ep 2495 - Raining Money
shortDesc: Taarak reads in the newspaper about a banking scam and informs it to Bhide, who calls up his bank manager to make sure his money is safe. One after the other bank officials arrive at Jethalal's house as Jethalal is taking a loan from the banks.

title: Ep 2496 - Off He Goes To The Island
shortDesc: Bhide assures Jethalal that bank is the safest place to invest in. Popatlal is in a hurry to file a fresh story on a banking scam. Meanwhile, Jethalal is ecstatic to learn that his loan has been sactioned.

title: Ep 2497 - Jethalals Foreign Trip
shortDesc: Bhide and Popatlal are intrigued seeing Jethalal in a hurry. Bhide suspects that Jethalal is committing a bank fraud and flying off to an island to escape payment of debt. Later, Jethalal finds that his house door is locked.

title: Ep 2498 - Jethalal Going Abroad
shortDesc: The news is spearing quickly among Gokuldham society that Jethalal is going to some foreign country for his business purpose. Madhabhi and Sodhi bid farewell to Jetha in a heartwarming way.

title: Ep 2499 - Comparison
shortDesc: As Jethalal flies off to an island on a business trip, Bhide cannot help but compare himself to Jethalal. Madhvi shows a mirror to Bhide and makes him look at the happiness in his life.

title: Ep 2500 - Jethalals 100 Crore Scam
shortDesc: Baga and Nattu Kaka inform Champaklal and Tappu that the police have sealed Gada Electronics as Jethalal has taken a loan of 100 crore rupees and flown away to Senorica Island.

title: Ep 2501 - The Scam That Rocked Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Inspector Pandey shows evidence of Jethalal's 100 crore scam to Gokuldham society members.

title: Ep 2502 - Police Interrogation
shortDesc: The police seal Jethalal's house. Then, Inspector Pandey takes the Gokuldham society members to the police station for interrogation. Popatlal is taken for interrogation first.

title: Ep 2503 - Evidence Against Jethalal
shortDesc: Inspector Pandey produces evidence against Jethalal. Seeing Jethalal partying, Champaklal feels dizzy.

title: Ep 2504 - What Has Jethalal Done?
shortDesc: As all the residents of Gokuldham society head to the police station to hear the news that Jethalal has called for a lawyer, they understand that he has done something or the other.

title: Ep 2505 - Time To Go
shortDesc: Bapu Ji and Tapu feel embarrassed and humiliated after Jethalal's entire facade so they decide to leave Gokuldham society. They try to contact Daya who has gone on a trip but couldn't connect with her.

title: Ep 2506 - Men In Black
shortDesc: Dada Ji and Tapu leave Gokuldham society to go to their village "Bachao" but on the way to the bus stop, they are stopped by two men in black who asks them to get into a car with them.

title: Ep 2507 - Jethalals New Avatar
shortDesc: Tappu and Champaklal meet Jethalal and extract the details of the bank fraud which he has committed. Then, a gun falls out of Jethalal's pocket. Champaklal picks up the gun and points it towards Jethalal.

title: Ep 2508 - Dream Or Reality
shortDesc: With all the fuss regarding Jethalal's scam, Chacha Ji wakes up in the morning and realizes that everything was just a dream but he gets worried when he is not able to get in contact with Jethalal.
